                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "electric_button"
                        },
                        {
                            Name: "None of those lead",
                            Actions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "COMMAND",
                                    ExecAsUser: 1b,
                                    Cmd: "tag @s add lead_shadow"
                                },
                                {
                                    Type: "COMMAND",
                                    ExecAsUser: 1b,
                                    Cmd: "tag @s add mm_declared"
                                },
                                {
                                    Type: "CLOSE_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "other_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Welcome to Mystic Marsh. I am Leader Titania. Fairy-types are gentle until the moment they are not — and this marsh likes to study a challenger before it tests one. So tell me plainly: who walks at the front of your party?"
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "The water here goes still as glass before every gym battle, and it asks the same question of everyone who leans over it. Which partner leads your line, challenger? Say it, and let the marsh listen."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Titania — the marsh asks",
                    Label: "declare"
                },
                {
                    Conditions: [
                        {
                            Type: "PLAYER_TAG",
                            Operation: "EQUALS",
                            Name: "defeated_mystic_apprentice"
                        },
                        {
                            Type: "PLAYER_TAG",
                            Operation: "EQUALS",
                            Name: "lead_fire"
                        }
                    ],
                    Priority: 16,
                    Buttons: [
                        {
                            Name: "Challenge the Gym",
                            Actions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "COMMAND",
                                    ConditionDataSet: {
                                        ConditionDataSet: [
                                            {
                                                Type: "PLAYER_TAG",
                                                Operation: "EQUALS",
                                                Name: "defeated_mystic_leader"
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    Cmd: "say You carry the Charm Badge. The marsh whispers your name when you walk it, you know. It has done that since before you arrived."
                                },
                                {
                                    Type: "COMMAND",
                                    ExecAsUser: 1b,
                                    ConditionDataSet: {
                                        ConditionDataSet: [
                                            {
                                                Type: "PLAYER_TAG",
                                                Operation: "EQUALS",
                                                Name: "no_defeated_mystic_leader"
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    Cmd: "cutscene play leader_intro function cobblemon_initiative:gym/engage_mystic_leader_mirror_fire"
                                },
                                {
                                    Type: "CLOSE_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "yes_button"
                        },
                        {
                            Name: "I need to prepare",
                            Actions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "CLOSE_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "leave_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "You lead with fire, so the marsh went looking for fire in me. Look at what surfaced beside my familiars — still water always sends back something of whoever leans over it. Come and fight what it made of you."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "A flame at your front. The mist has been drinking its light since you declared it, and now something at my side flickers the same way. The marsh shows every challenger a piece of themselves. This piece is yours."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Titania — mirror challenge",
                    Label: "mirror_fire"
                },
                {
                    Conditions: [
                        {
                            Type: "PLAYER_TAG",
                            Operation: "EQUALS",
                            Name: "defeated_mystic_apprentice"
