                            Label: "yes_button"
                        },
                        {
                            Name: "I need to prepare",
                            Actions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "CLOSE_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "leave_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "You lead with grass. The reeds heard you say it, and something green and glowing rose out of the shallows to stand with me. The marsh shows every challenger a piece of themselves — this one is yours."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Roots speak to roots. Your lead has been whispering to the marsh since you crossed the first bridge, and the marsh grew an answer into my line. See if you recognize it."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Titania — mirror challenge",
                    Label: "mirror_grass"
                },
                {
